OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,FPublic safety could be at risk as
OL,7,FJersey's La Moye Prison fails to make
OL,8,Fprobation support for released
OL,9,Fprisoners mandatory, inspectors warn.
OL,11,FThe HM Chief Inspector of Prisons'
OL,12,Fprevious assessment seven years ago
OL,13,Frecommended 60 areas for improvement
OL,14,Fbut less than half have been achieved
OL,15,Fto date.
