OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,FThe latest review shows staff are
OL,7,Fstill monitoring prisoners with
OL,8,Fcameras when they are showering and
OL,9,Fusing the toilet, not giving inmates
OL,10,Faccess to complaints procedures, and
OL,11,Foffering little support for those who
OL,12,Fare neurodiverse.
OL,14,FWhile the report praises La Moye for
OL,15,Fits "excellent staff-prisoner
OL,16,Frelationships" and overall safety, it
OL,17,Fcriticises the "significant
OL,18,Fdeterioration" of work and education
OL,19,Fprovision to prevent reoffending upon
OL,20,Frelease.
