OL,6,FSignificantly, the report states:
OL,7,F"There was no mandatory post-release
OL,8,Fprobation supervision for most adult
OL,9,Fprisoners, which potentially
OL,10,Fundermined public protection."
OL,12,FOther recommendations not achieved
OL,13,Ffrom 2017 include:
OL,15,FHowever, the prison is praised for
OL,16,F"little violence" and low self-harm
OL,17,Frates, with the fact that there were
OL,18,Fno recorded incidents of self-harm by
OL,19,Fwomen last year described as
OL,20,F"unprecedented".
