OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,FAndrew Neilson from the Howard League
OL,7,Ffor Penal Reform says that while there
OL,8,Fwere positives from the inspection,
OL,9,Fthe lack of purposeful activity and
OL,10,Fpreparation for people on release is
OL,11,Fworrying.
OL,13,FAndrew explains: "When you have
OL,14,Fsomeone in prison, they are literally
OL,15,Fa captive audience.
