OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,F"Simply expecting somebody to lie on a
OL,7,Fprison bunk all day doing nothing is
OL,8,Fnot going to turn a life around. It's
OL,9,Fnot going to help someone get away
OL,10,Ffrom crime and move away from
OL,11,Foffending.
OL,13,F"Purposeful activity - things like
OL,14,Fwork and education - these are the key
OL,15,Fto helping people desist from crime
OL,16,Fand ensure that they don't re-offend
OL,17,Fon release."
