OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,FAndrew adds that Jersey suffers from
OL,7,Fbeing a smaller jurisdiction with a
OL,8,Flack of external institutions offering
OL,9,Fadditional funding and data.
OL,11,FHe concludes: "There are definitely
OL,12,Fsome limitations for La Moye in that
OL,13,Fregard, but the Jersey Government
OL,14,Fshould certainly be looking at what it
OL,15,Fcan do to address the issues that the
OL,16,Finspector has raised."
