OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,FJersey's Justice and Home Affairs
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Mary Le Hegarat, says
OL,8,Fthe number one focus is to make La
OL,9,FMoye "a really good education
OL,10,Ffacility".
OL,12,FShe explains: "The report highlights
OL,13,Fthe positive management that is
OL,14,Factually at the prison and it seems to
OL,15,Fbe positive from the perspective of
OL,16,Fprisoners as well.
OL,18,F"When somebody ends up for whatever
OL,19,Freason in La Moye Prison, we need to
OL,20,Fensure that they're still going to get
OL,21,Fan education.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
