OL,3,CInspectors find prison procedures
OL,4,Ccould risk public safety
OL,6,F"If we can get some really good
OL,7,Feducational programs in place - and
OL,8,Fthey've started to work on a new
OL,9,Fcurriculum for 2025 - then that means
OL,10,Fwhen they are released from prison,
OL,11,Fthey'll be able to hopefully get a job
OL,12,Fwhich will change the whole dynamic of
OL,13,Fthe way forward for them for the
OL,14,Ffuture."
